    "global": "Write vowels_count using s.lower() normalization, a set-membership count over {'a','e','i','o','u'}, a conditional +1 for trailing 'y', then add 13 assert-based test cases covering the docstring, y-position variants, empty string, all-consonants, and all-vowels inputs.",
